1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:09,746
Madam Liu didn't bleed — she burst into black smoke. Everyone saw it. Everyone kept quiet. That's how a demon dies.

2
00:00:10,146 --> 00:00:13,599
I need time — time to figure out what's inside this body.

3
00:00:13,999 --> 00:00:18,477
Myriad-Demon Bloodline System. Level 1. Warning: if your demon awakening tops 50%, you lose your mind — for good.

4
00:00:18,877 --> 00:00:21,290
Refining Madam Liu's leftover demon blood... Done. EXP +10.

5
00:00:21,690 --> 00:00:26,563
Jade Demon Rank unlocked. Body +100%, Speed +80%, Senses +50%. New skill: Demonic Aura.

6
00:00:26,963 --> 00:00:28,251
Okay, that's just ridiculous.

7
00:00:28,651 --> 00:00:29,654
Demonic Aura — on.

8
00:00:30,054 --> 00:00:35,618
That black cat out back? Lowest-tier spirit. The woman in the west wing — human.

9
00:00:36,018 --> 00:00:40,965
Three of them under the locust tree... and something big at the bottom of that well.

10
00:00:41,365 --> 00:00:49,135
The cold palace is a hunting ground. The fallen concubines? They're the prey.

11
00:00:49,535 --> 00:00:54,568
No wonder they keep "dying of illness" and vanishing.

12
00:00:54,968 --> 00:00:57,333
My lady... you look amazing today.

13
00:00:57,733 --> 00:01:03,031
Get some sleep tonight. Whatever you hear — don't come out.

14
00:01:03,431 --> 00:01:05,146
My lady, what are you going to do?

15
00:01:05,546 --> 00:01:06,140
Hunt demons.
